snippet: DeMar DeRozan scored 32 points, including a key 3-pointer late, and grabbed 13 rebounds as the Toronto Raptors defeated the Washington Wizards 114-106 on Friday night despite giving back a 19-point first-half lead....

headline.main: DeRozan, Powell Lead Raptors Past Wizards 114-106
headline.print_headline: DeRozan, Powell Lead Raptors Past Wizards 114-106

lead_paragraph: DeMar DeRozan scored 32 points, including a key 3-pointer late, and grabbed 13 rebounds as the Toronto Raptors defeated the Washington Wizards 114-106 on Friday night despite giving back a 19-point first-half lead.
